ot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">At 11:30 in August 23rd - 11:50; 15:20-15:40</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">At 11:00 in August 24th - 11:20</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">At the same time, Parallels also prepares exquisite gift bags for the media and audience friends visiting the Parallels booth first. You are welcome to take part in the collection. To get more information about Parallels, let&#39;s go to the Parallels Macworld booth at the National Conference Center in August 21st.</span></p><p><br/></p>', 48, 49, 0, 0, 0, 0, '../upload/201801/1515739663.jpg', '', 0, '', 2, '2018-1-12 16:03:29', '2018-1-12 16:03:29', 0, 0, '', 'en', 0, 1, '', '');
